| Tools That Manage Both Macs and PCs                                |
|   from the one-tool-to-rule-them-all dept.                         |
|   posted by kdawson on Tuesday June 12, @18:18 (Software)          |
|   http://it.slashdot.org/article.pl?sid=07/06/12/2021247           |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

johannacw writes "Ryan Faas takes a look at [0]nine tools that handle
system management tasks in both Mac and Windows environments for both
clients and servers. The tools span a range of tasks such as remote
installation, license management, and helpdesk functions. The author
gives opinions on each tool's strengths and weaknesses and does not pick
an overall winner."

